
~ RECIPE for Running FireFox OS ("v1.1.0hd" branch) on Pandaboard ES ~ 


1. To Build: 

export CC=/opt/gcc-4.4.7/bin/gcc
export CXX=/opt/gcc-4.4.7/bin/g++

cd B2G 
./build.sh -j(n) 


2. To Flash: 

[Plug in *only* USB mini cable] 

device/ti/panda/usbboot device/ti/panda/bootloader.bin 

[Now insert SD Card] 

fastboot oem format
fastboot flash xloader device/ti/panda/xloader.bin
fastboot flash bootloader device/ti/panda/bootloader.bin
./flash.sh 

[Use Serial-to-USB cable to run Gtkterm or Minicom.] 

